_sText:
I started this map during summer 2014 but I slacked as fuck but I also improved the map with new ideas. I decided to finally release it, but it is not as I wanted.

This map contains :

  • 21 traps
  • 2 secret smokegrenades
  • 5 endings (AWP, bhop, deagle, punish and knife)
  • 64 slots (60 CTs and 4 Ts)
  • Music (Ceadeus Theme from Monster Hunter 3)
